data.description: New Roof! Nice single level townhouse in southwest Amarillo. 2 bedrooms with nice sized closets. The guest bedroom has a Jack-n-Jill style bathroom. The townhouse has a sunroom, formal dining, sprinkler system, and a  nice sized two car garage.
